Package edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.number.real Description

An implementation of the number module. External users of this module should not import elements from here. Instead, import elements of the IF package.

This implementation uses a representation of integers that uses Java's BigInteger class. Rational numbers are represented as an ordered pair (numerator,denominator) of big integers, with GCD 1.
